n%20live%20in%20a%20city%20like%20New%20York%20and%20still%20feel%20very%20alone%2C%20even%20living%20with%20three%20roommates%20and%20sharing%20a%20bathroom%2C%26quot%3B%20Ball%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2266ff9ae0-d9c6-4a5c-b0ab-605245fe270a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoving%20to%20the%20Midwest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBall%20got%20to%20see%20what%20Indianapolis%20was%20like%20when%20she%20visited%20her%20mom%20while%20she%20was%20on%20a%20work%20assignment%20as%20a%20travel%20nurse%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20just%20something%20really%20charming%20about%20the%20city%2C%26quot%3B%20Ball%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBall%20was%20also%20considering%20furthering%20her%20education%20around%20this%20time.%20She%20said%20she%20came%20across%20an%20ad%20about%20the%20Indiana%20University%20Lilly%20Family%20School%20of%20Philanthropy%20during%20this%20visit.%20She%20moved%20to%20Indianapolis%20shortly%20before%20pursuing%20a%20master's%20in%20philanthropic%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20going%20through%20a%20career%20transition%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20she%20had%20been%20in%20the%20fashion%20industry%20for%20several%20years%2C%20including%20as%20an%20undergraduate%20in%20New%20York%20City%20and%20while%20working%20in%20Italy%20after%20graduating.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20kind%20of%20gravitating%20towards%20the%20more%20socially%20impactful%20side%20of%20the%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20feeling%20of%20home%20was%20one%20thing%20that%20drew%20her%20to%20Indianapolis.%20%26quot%3BThe%20architecture%20in%20Indianapolis%20is%20very%20similar%20to%20the%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20something%20about%20that%20environment%20that%20just%20made%20it%20feel%20like%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20professional%20opportunities%20also%20drew%20her%20to%20the%20city.%20Ball%20recently%20completed%20her%20master's%20and%20has%20been%20working%20for