%20is%20worth%20an%20estimated%20%241.3%20trillion%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.grandviewresearch.com%2Findustry-analysis%2Fluxury-travel-market%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpected%20to%20grow%207.9%25%20from%202024%20to%202030%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuxury%20travelers%20are%20not%20necessarily%20looking%20for%20the%20best%20deals%20but%20the%20best%20way%20to%20plan%20a%20trip%20without%20the%20hassle.%20This%20is%20where%20a%20luxury-travel%20advisor%20comes%20in.%20Agents%20can%20provide%20personalized%20itineraries%2C%20access%20to%20upgrades%20and%20selective%20experiences%2C%20and%20support%20throughout%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20talked%20to%20three%20luxury-travel%20advisors%20about%20the%20industry's%20growth%20and%20how%20to%20transition%20into%20travel%20advising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d0bc394b-7621-4fa4-a0f8-32d935c8b8b2%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20luxury-travel%20industry%20is%20booming%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDiana%20Hechler%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dtourstravel.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ED.%20Tours%20Travel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20the%20luxury-travel%20industry%20has%20grown%20because%20travelers%20have%20access%20to%20more%20luxury-level%20properties%2C%20and%20more%20people%20are%20willing%20to%20pay%20luxury%20prices.%20Also%2C%20a%20vacation%20is%20seen%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcook-chef-manager-amusement-parks-gen-z-attendant-experience-economy2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20necessity%20for%20Gen%20Z%20travelers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20booking%20vacations%20more%20than%20ever%20and%20want%20them%20to%20be%20stress-free%20and%20restorative.%20And%20nothing%20does%20that%20better%20than%20luxury%20travel%2C%26quot%3B%20Hechler%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BDespite%20the%20higher%20prices%2C%20the%20segment%20of%20travelers%20that%20want%20luxury%20and%20are%20willing%20to%20pay%20for%20it%20has%20grown%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Diana%20Hechler%20smiling%20against%20the%20backdrop%20on%20a%20scenic%20landscape%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66758ae4886e840164beb8e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDiana%20Hechler%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20D.%20Tours%20Travel.%3Cp%3ED.%20Tours%20Travel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAngela%20Adto%20Tepper%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.azaluxurytravel.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAZA%20Luxury%20Travel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20the%20shift%20toward%20luxury%20travel%20had%20increased%20since%20the%20pandemic%2C%20with%20more%20Americans%20prioritizing%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20luxury-travel%20sector%20has%20evolved%20to%20prioritize%20wellness%2C%20health%2C%20sustainability%2C%20and%20transformative%20experiences%2C%20and%20people%20are%20now%20prioritizing%20meaningful%20travel%20experiences%20and%20pursuing%20bucket-list%20trips%2C%26quot%3B%20Tepper%20said.%20%26quot%3BAdvisors%20have%20adapted%20by%20curating%20journeys%20tailored%20to%20each%20client.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e8bab25d-5ff3-4403-9e08-2486bf69f866%5C%22%3EWhy%20travelers%20work%20with%20advisors%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20advantages%20of%20working%20with%20a%20travel%20advisor%20is%20that%20it%20helps%20travelers%20cut%20through%20the%20noise%20and%20information%20overload.%20Traveler%20agents%20work%20on%20commission%2C%20getting%20a%20percentage%20of%20hotel%2C%20cruise%2C%20or%20tour%20costs%2C%20which%20is%20paid%20after%20a%20trip%20is%20over.%20Many%20agents%20also%20charge%20an%20up-front%20fee%20for%20research%20and%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20internet%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20death%20of%20advisors%2C%20and%20instead%2C%20it's%20made%20us%20more%20valuable%20than%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20Hechler%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20some%20people%20love%20to%20spend%20time%20researching%20their%20vacations%20and%20doing%20it%20themselves%2C%20many%20don't%20have%20time%20to%20'waste'%20on%20the%20internet%20starting%20from%20scratch.%20Saving%20time%20is%20problem-solving%20for%20almost%20everyone%3B%20anytime%20you%20can%20solve%20people's%20problems%2C%20you%20can%20have%20a%20successful%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETravel%20advisors%20can%20also%20offer%20complimentary%20upgrades%20and%20have%20access%20to%20experiences%20that%20might%20not%20be%20available%20to%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorking%20with%20a%20travel%20advisor%20can%20be%20summarized%20by%20three%20E's%2C%26quot%3B%20Tepper%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20provide%20expertise%20and%20insider%20knowledge%2C%20extras%20with%20personalized%20service%2C%20and%20emergency%20assistance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Angela%20Adto%20Tepper%20headshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66758a92886e840164beb8b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAngela%20Adto%20Tepper%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20AZA%20Luxury%20Travel.%3Cp%3EAZA%20Luxury%20Travel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20prevalence%20of%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok%2C%20it%20might%20seem%20like%20everyone%20is%20going%20to%20the%20same%20places.%20So%20booking%20luxury%20hotels%20or%20making%20reservations%20at%20Michelin-starred%20restaurants%20is%20no%20longer%20enough%3B%20travelers%20want%20advisors%20to%20curate%20one-of-a-kind%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20luxury-travel%20sector%20is%20not%20just%20about%20opulence%20and%20indulgence%20but%20also%20about%20creating%20meaningful%2C%20enriching%20experiences%20that%20leave%20a%20lasting%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20Maurice%20Smith%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20luxury-travel%20agency%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eugenetoriko.com%2Fabout%2Fmauricesmith%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEugene%20Toriko%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BSustainable%20and%20regenerative%20travel%20practices%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20important%2C%20focusing%20on%20preserving%20and%20enhancing%20the%20destinations%20we%20visit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b6f140b-dd8b-4170-8551-bcd2b8a53375%5C%22%3ETips%20for%20transitioning%20into%20travel%20advising%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20ready%20to%20move%20into%20the%20industry%2C%20it's%20worth%20taking%20stock%20of%20your%20skills%20first.%20For%20example%2C%20Tepper%20said%20people%20with%20event-planning%20experience%20might%20transition%20well%20into%20travel%20advising%20since%20itinerary%20planning%20and%20familiarity%20with%20booking%20platforms%20are%20part%20of%20the%20job.%20She%20added%20that%20soft%20skills%2C%20like%20interpersonal%20communication%2C%20problem-solving%2C%20and%20adaptability%2C%20would%20also%20come%20in%20handy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETepper%20recommended%20contacting%20an%20advisor%20before%20switching%20over.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20considering%20the%20career%20change%2C%20one%20of%20the%20best%20things%20you%20can%20do%20is%20secure%20a%20reputable%20mentor%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20mentor%20can%20offer%20invaluable%20guidance%2C%20accelerating%20professional%20growth%20and%20enhancing%20skill%20development%2C%20leading%20to%20greater%20success%20and%20higher%20earnings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20helps%20to%20study%20travel%20trends%2C%20have%20a%20deep%20knowledge%20of%20a%20destination%2C%20and%20build%20expertise%20around%20types%20of%20travel%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmultigenerational-family-cruise-vacation-kids-grandmother-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultigenerational%20trips%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20cruises%2C%20or%20honeymoons.%20Tepper%20said%20that%20prospective%20advisors%20must%20also%20remember%20that%20they're%20not%20necessarily%20looking%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%20discounts%26quot%3B%20for%20clients%20but%20creating%20tailored%20trips%20with%20impeccable%20customer%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20maintain%20the%20quality%20of%20our%20personalized%20work%2C%20we%20occasionally%20have%20to%20turn%20away%20a%20client%2C%26quot%3B%20Tepper%20said.%20%26quot%3BNot%20every%20client%20is%20the%20right%20fit%20for%20our%20service.%20This%20selectivity%20ensures%20that%20we%20can%20devote%20the%20necessary%20time%20and%20attention%20to%20crafting%20great%20experiences%20for%20everyone%20while%20upholding%20the%20high%20standards%20we%20have%20put%20in%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2220ff0366-89dc-464a-b1bb-6d985f7819cf%5C%22%3EThe%20benefits%20of%20travel%20advising%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETravel%20advising%20provides%20valuable%20services%20to%20travelers%2C%20but%20agents%20can%20also%20receive%20perks%20like%20complimentary%20trips%20sponsored%20by%20hotels%20and%20tourism%20boards%20and%20travel%20discounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20perks%20of%20this%20job%20is%20the%20opportunity%20to%20explore%20the%20world%20and%20indulge%20in%20my%20passion%20for%20travel%2C%26quot%3B%20Tepper%20said.%20%26quot%3BImagine%20waking%20up%20in%20a%20new%20city%2C%20tasting%20exotic%20cuisines%2C%20and%20immersing%20yourself%20in%20diverse%20cultures%20while%20doing%20what%20you%20love.%20For%20me%2C%20it's%20a%20career%20that%20blends%20passion%20and%20purpose.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20few%20challenges.%20Smith%20said%20that%20agents%20must%20stay%20on%20top%20of%20ever-changing%20travel%20regulations%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20their%20clients.%20But%20ultimately%2C%20he%20said%2C%20it's%20a%20rewarding%20career%20that%20prioritizes%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTravel%20advising%20offers%20flexibility%20and%20the%20potential%20to%20work%20remotely%2C%20allowing%20for%20a%20good%20work-life%20balance%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%20%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20helping%20clients%20create%20unforgettable%20memories%20and%20the%20joy%20of%20turning%20their%20travel%20dreams%20into%20reality%20is%20incredibly%20rewarding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-travel-advisors-on-industry-popularity-career-opportunities-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719494448000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667c64b2d1c84a0eaca80fbf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-travel-advisors-on-industry-popularity-career-opportunities-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Luxury-travel%20advisors%20are%20seeing%20a%20growth%20in%20demand%20as%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennial%20travelers%20look%20to%20enjoy%20convenient%20planning%20for%20fun%20travel%20experiences.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Mariette%20Williams)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-travel-advisors-on-industry-popularity-career-opportunities-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22EU%20leaders%20to%20agree%20on%20top%20jobs%20despite%20Meloni%20discontent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719494275000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1652%2Flive%2F60123940-3480-11ef-a53b-67ee534ca28a.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc720jxw2rn8o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Italian%20leader%20ha