%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnother%20delay%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20announced%20on%20Friday.%20The%20aviation%20company%20said%20it%20needed%20time%20to%20schedule%20two%20spacewalks%20and%20to%20assess%20issues%20on%20board%20following%20five%20helium%20leaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-nasa-starliner-astronauts-stuck-in-space-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20previously%20reported%2C%20helium%20supports%20Starlink's%20reaction%20control%20system%20thrusters%2C%20which%20allows%20them%20to%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F0a2ab3bc-03cc-499c-82f8-50cfe1a52103%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Boeing%20said%20the%20delays%20were%20not%20considered%20a%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20test%20flight%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20mission%20is%20still%20going%20and%20it%20is%20going%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20company%20told%20BI%20that%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Bextended%20the%20mission%20in%20order%20to%20collect%20more%20data%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20helium%20leaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20the%20helium%20systems%20and%20thrusters%20are%20located%20in%20the%20spacecraft's%20service%20module%2C%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Bdiscarded%20and%20burns%20up%20in%20the%20atmosphere%20on%20reentry%2C%26quot%3B%20preventing%20a%20failure%20analysis%20from%20taking%20place%20on%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20added%20that%20the%20helium%20leaks%20had%20been%20fixed%20and%20were%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20concern%20for%20the%20return%20mission%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20four%20of%20the%20five%20thrusters%20were%20operating%20normally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStarliner%20is%20performing%20well%20in%20orbit%20while%20docked%20to%20the%20space%20station%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperso