.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc9785924je3o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc9785924je3o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20%26quot%3BSecret%20Meeting%26quot%3B%20Quip%20On%20Lift%20Encounter%20With%20D%20Fadnavis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20accidental%20meeting%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20Maharashtra%20Assembly's%20monsoon%20session%2C%20arch-rivals%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20found%20themselves%20waiting%20for%20the%20lift%20together.%20Awkwardness%20was%20in%20the%20air%2C%20and%20a%20video%20that%20has%20now%20gone%20viral%20shows%20the%20two%20former%20Chief%20Ministers%20exchanging%20some%20words%3B%20the%20mood%20is%20cold%20at%20best.%20While%20what%20they%20spoke%20about%20is%20not%20known%2C%20the%20body%20language%20suggests%20that%20it%20was%20little%20more%20than%20small%20talk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20conversation%20when%20he%20interacted%20with%20the%20media%20later.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20here%20on%2C%20we%20will%20do%20all%20our%20secret%20meetings%20in%20the%20lift%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20joked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Devendraji%20and%20I%20were%20in%20the%20lift%2C%20people%20must%20have%20thought%20of%20the%20song%2C%20'na%20na%20karte%20pyar%20tumhi%20se%20kar%20baithe'%20(a%20classic%20from%20the%201965%20film%20Jab%20Jab%20Phool%20Khile%20that%20roughly%20translates%20to%20'I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20you%20despite%20denials).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20nothing%20like%20that.%20It%20was%20an%20unexpected%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20chief%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20gave%20the%20incident%20a%20different%20spin.%20%26quot%3BTwo%20years%20ago%2C%20they%20(Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20his%20team)%20took%20a%20different%20lift%20and%20went%20to%20the%20Congress.%20We%20took%20one%20that%20carried%20us%20to%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20light-hearted%20interaction%2C%20pictures%20of%20which%20have%20emerged%2C%20was%20between%20BJP%20minister%20Chandrakant%20Patil%20and%20Mr%20Thackeray.%20When%20the%20BJP%20leader%20gave%20a%20bar%20of%20chocolate%20to%20Mr%20Thackeray%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BTomorrow%20you%20will%20give%20chocolate%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Maharashtra.%26quot%3B%20The%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20was%20clearly%20referring%20to%20the%20state%20budget%20that%20is%20likely%20to%20offer%20sops%20to%20woo%20voters%20ahead%20of%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20last%20Assembly%20session%20before%20the%20Maharashtra%20election%20due%20later%20this%20year.%20These%20polls%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20tight%20contest%20after%20the%20MVA%20trumped%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20of%20BJP%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Eknath%20Shinde)%20and%20NCP%20(Ajit%20Pawar)%20in%20this%20general%20election.%20Out%20of%20the%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20the%20MVA%20won%2030%20and%20the%20NDA%20bloc%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20upcoming%20election%20is%20significant%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20splits%20in%20two%20key%20political%20forces%20in%20the%20state%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years.%20In%20the%20last%20state%20election%20in%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20undivided%20Shiv%20Sena%20fought%20in%20alliance%20and%20secured%20a%20majority.%20But%20the%20allies%20fell%20out%20over%20rotational%20chiefministership%20and%20Mr%20Thackeray%20tied%20up%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20to%20form%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20government%20was%20toppled%20after%20his%20trusted%20lieutenant%20Eknath%20Shinde%20led%20a%20mutiny%20that%20split%20the%20Shiv%20Sena.%20Mr%20Shinde%20tied%20up%20with%20the%20BJP%20to%20form%20the%20next%20government.%20Subsequently%2C%20NCP%20leader%20Ajit%20Pawar%20rebelled%20against%20his%20uncle%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20split%20in%20NCP.%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20too%2C%20joined%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719490740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F7camhtto_uddhav-fadnavis-lift_625x300_27_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuddhav-thackeray-devendra-fadnavis-uddhav-thackerays-secret-meeting-quip-on-lift-encounter-with-d-fadnavis-5981292%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20accidental%20meeting%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20Maharashtra%20Assembly's%20monsoon%20session%2C%20arch-rivals%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20found%20themselves%20waiting%20for%20the%20lift%20together.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuddhav-thackeray-devendra-fadnavis-uddhav-thackerays-secret-meeting-quip-on-lift-encounter-with-d-fadnavis-5981292%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuddhav-thackeray-devendra-fadnavis-uddhav-thackerays-secret-meeting-quip-on-lift-encounter-with-d-fadnavis-5981292%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuddhav-thackeray-devendra-fadnavis-uddhav-thackerays-secret-meeting-quip-on-lift-encounter-with-d-fadnavis-5981292%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bolivia's%20failed%20coup%20attempt...%20in%2075%20seconds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719490739000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F8c9c%2Flive%2F5f082e30-347e-11ef-bdc5-41d7421c2adf.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc2e4pv9zdmpo%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20all%20started%20when%20the%20presidential%20palace%20in%20La%20Paz%20was%20stormed%20by%20soldiers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3