2%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fce7812ej0k1o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fce7812ej0k1o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPride%20Of%20Every%20Tamilian%26quot%3B%3A%20Minister%20Attacks%20Opposition%20Over%20'Sengol'%20Demand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition's%20push%20to%20keep%20the%20Constitution%20front%20and%20centre%20by%20asking%20for%20the%20'sengol'%2C%20a%20sceptre%20kept%20next%20to%20the%20Speaker's%20chair%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20to%20be%20replaced%20by%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20text%20has%20led%20to%20a%20strong%20pushback%20by%20the%20government%2C%20which%20has%20accused%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20of%20disrespecting%20the%20baton%20and%20what%20it%20symbolises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MP%20RK%20Chaudhary%20writing%20to%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20and%20asking%20for%20the%20'sengol'%20to%20be%20replaced%20by%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20junior%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20L%20Murugan%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20sceptre%20is%20the%20pride%20of%20every%20Tamilian.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20also%20mentioned%20in%20Tirukkural%20(a%20classic%20Tamil%20text%20by%20poet%20and%20philosopher%20Thiruvalluvar)%2C%20which%20spoke%20about%20how%20the%20sengol%20plays%20a%20role%20in%20government.%20When%20India%20got%20freedom%2C%20(Governor%20General)%20Mountbatten%20and%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20had%20spoken%20about%20how%20power%20would%20be%20handed%20over%20after%20Independence%20and%20when%20Rajaji%20(C%20Rajagopalachari)%20was%20consulted%2C%20he%20said%20it%20can%20be%20done%20using%20a%20sengol%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Murugan%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20former%20president%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20BJP%2C%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five-foot-long%20sceptre%2C%20made%20of%20gold%2C%20was%20commissioned%20by%20the%20Thiruvavaduthurai%20Adheenam%20(math%20pontiff)%20and%20sent%20to%20Delhi.%20The%20minister%20said%20that%20the%20'sengol'%20was%20given%20to%20%C2%A0Nehru%20after%20conducting%20rituals%20but%20it%20%26quot%3Bwas%20not%20valued%26quot%3B%20and%20sent%20somewhere.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%2C%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20found%20out%20where%20the%20'sengol'%20was%20kept%20(Allahabad%20Museum)%20and%20brought%20it%20to%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building.%20It%20was%20installed%20in%20the%20new%20Parliament%20after%20rituals%20were%20conducted%20by%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Adheenams.%20The%20sengol%20symbolises%20a%20fair%20government.%20The%20INDIA%20alliance%20does%20not%20value%20the%20sengol.%20Its%20attitude%20is%20condemnable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Mr%20Chaudhary%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20MP%20from%20Mohanlalganj%2C%20had%20sparked%20a%20row%20by%20asking%20for%20the%20'sengol'%20to%20be%20replaced%20to%20%26quot%3Bsave%20democracy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20adoption%20of%20the%20Constitution%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20democracy%20in%20the%20country%2C%20and%20the%20Constitution%20is%20its%20symbol.%20The%20BJP%20government%20in%20its%20last%20term%20installed%20'sengol'%20next%20to%20the%20Speaker's%20chair.%20Sengol%20is%20a%20Tamil%20word%20that%20means%20sceptre.%20Rajdand%20also%20means%20the%20king's%20stick.%20We%20have%20become%20independent%20after%20the%20age%20of%20kings.%20Now%2C%20every%20man%20and%20woman%20who%20is%20an%20eligible%20voter%20chooses%20the%20government%20to%20run%20this%20country.%20So%20will%20the%20country%20run%20by%20Constitution%20or%20by%20a%20king's%20stick%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20SP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20demand%20was%20backed%20by%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20and%20MP%20B%20Manickam%20Tagore%2C%20an%20MP%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20who%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20very%20clear%20that%20the%20'sengol'%20symbolises%20kingship%20and%20the%20kingdom-era%20is%20over.%20We%20should%20celebrate%20the%20people's%20democracy%20and%20the%20Constitution.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20said%20the%20demand%20reflects%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20%26quot%3Bhatred%26quot%3B%20for%20Tamil%20culture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSamajwadi%20Party%20has%20no%20respect%20for%20Indian%20history%20or%20culture.%20The%20remarks%20of%20their%20top%20leaders%20on%20the%20Sengol%20are%20condemnable%20and%20indicate%20their%20ignorance.%20It%20also%20shows%20INDI%20Alliance's%20hatred%20to%20Tamil%20culture%20in%20particular%20The%20Sengol%20is%20India's%20pride%20and%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20honour%20that%20Hon.%20PM%20Shri%20%40narendramodi%20Ji%20accorded%20it%20the%20highest%20respect%20in%20the%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'sengol'%20was%20installed%20in%20the%20new%20Parliament%20on%20May%2028%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719490500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fnsf1uo3_l-murugan_625x300_27_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpride-of-every-tamilian-minister-attacks-opposition-over-sengol-demand-5982498%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20opposition's%20push%20to%20keep%20the%20Constitution%20front%20and%20centre%20by%20asking%20for%20the%20'sengol'%2C%20a%20sceptre%20kept%20next%20to%20the%20Speaker's%20chair%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20to%20be%20replaced%20by%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20text%20has%20led%20to%20a%20strong%20pushback%20by%20the%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpride-of-every-tamilian-minister-attacks-opposition-over-sengol-demand-5982498%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2F