c%20Air%20Show%20on%20September%2029%2C%202023%20in%20HUNTINGTON%20BEACH%2C%20CA.%3Cp%3ENick%20Ut%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERare%20earth%20minerals%20are%20critical%20for%20national%20defense%20and%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENational%20stockpile%20levels%20are%20a%20mystery%2C%20though.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnd%20there%20are%20indications%20that%20the%20stockpile%20is%20insufficient%2C%20worrying%20experts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERare%20earth%20minerals%20are%20needed%20to%20make%20all%20sorts%20of%20things%2C%20from%20F-35%20stealth%20fighters%20and%20night-vision%20goggles%20to%20internet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencenews.org%2Farticle%2Frare-earth-elements-properties-technology%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiber-optic%20cables%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20MRI%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20a%20subset%20of%20the%20critical%20minerals%20deemed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.house.gov%2F_cache%2Ffiles%2Ff%2F3%2Ff3916ab1-1d9b-428c-9f81-bbc33d9b5b55%2F501924497A34C21E5EF3C335F2BE370C.division-z---energy-act.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eessential%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20national%20security.%20If%20the%20supply%20chain%20for%20these%20minerals%20is%20disrupted%2C%20the%20negative%20impact%20on%20the%20US%20could%20be%20considerable.%20Stockpile%20sizes%20are%20unclear%2C%20yet%20there%20are%20indications%20that%20levels%20aren't%20where%20they%20need%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20military's%20mission%20at%20home%20is%20to%20keep%20stockpiles%20of%20goods%20like%20critical%20minerals%20on%20hand%20for%20emergency%20wartime%20use.%20Recent%20government%20research%20suggests%20that%20Congress%20knows%20that%20the%20stockpile%20levels%20are%20insufficient%2C%20but%20the%20numbers%20aren't%20made%20available%20to%20the%20public.%20That%20opacity%20is%20troubling%20to%20some%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cdfc12aa-a8e0-4e53-ab72-b161a1e1acea%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20the%20dark%20on%20the%20stockpile%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20name%20suggests%20otherwise%2C%20rare%20earth%20minerals%20are%20not%20exactly%20rare%20%E2%80%94%20in%20fact%2C%20they're%20relatively%20plentiful.%20But%20finding%20them%20in%20large%20enough%20deposits%20to%20mine%20is%20difficult%2C%20and%20the%20refining%20process%2C%20separating%20the%20minerals%20while%20they're%20bound%20up%20in%20chunks%20of%20ore%2C%20is%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Fchinas-rare-earths-dominance-focus-after-mineral-export-curbs-2023-07-05%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edominates%20global%20markets%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20mining%20critical%20minerals%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Fscience%2Frare-earth-element%2FProcessing-ores%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elabor-intensive%20refining%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20challenge%20for%20the%20US%20given%20its%20rivalry%20with%20China%20and%20dependence%20on%20the%20minerals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20began%20cutting%20American%20imports%20of%20Chinese%20rare%20earth%20minerals%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20decrease%20US%20reliance%20on%20China%20for%20critical%20minerals.%20More%20recently%2C%20the%20White%20House%20initiated%20a%20push%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2022%2F02%2F22%2Ffact-sheet-securing-a-made-in-america-supply-chain-for-critical-minerals%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforge%20new%20partnerships%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20allies%20for%20mining%20and%20to%20boost%20mining%20investments%20within%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%20say%20the%20lack%20of%20transparency%20on%20mineral%20stockpile%20levels%20within%20the%20US%20leaves%20the%20public%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20what's%20actually%20being%20done%20to%20curb%20American%20dependence%20on%20what%20the%20Pentagon%20calls%20its%20%26quot%3Bpacing%20challenge%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20critical%20minerals%20it%20would%20need%20in%20a%20great-power%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20new%20Lockheed%20Martin%20F-35A%20Lightning%20ll%20multirole%20fighter%20jet%20parked%20in%20a%20hangar%20as%20it%20is%20presented%20to%20media%20at%20the%20Lockheed%20Martin%20factory%20in%20Fort%20Worth.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667acda9d1c84a0eaca77e35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20new%20Lockheed%20Martin%20F-35A%20Lightning%20ll%20multirole%20fighter%20jet%20parked%20in%20a%20hangar%20as%20it%20is%20presented%20to%20media%20at%20the%20Lockheed%20Martin%20factory%20in%20Fort%20Worth.%3Cp%3EOrjan%20F.%20Ellingvag%2FCorbis%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpayneinstitute.mines.edu%2Fproject%2Fgregory-wischer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGregory%20Wischer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20serves%20as%20a%20mineral%20consultant%20for%20Dei%20Gratia%20Minerals%20and%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnps.edu%2Fweb%2Feag%2Festimating-shortfalls-for-military-materials%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewritten%20extensively%20about%20critical%20minerals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20suspects%20national%20stockpile%20levels%20are%20well%20below%20where%20they%20should%20be%20given%20the%20available%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20has%20broad%20authority%20to%20dictate%20to%20the%20Defense%20Logistics%20Agency%20how%20much%20minerals%20they%20should%20stockpile%20and%20which%20minerals%20they%20should%20be%20stockpiling%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense's%20consumption%20rates%20of%20critical%20minerals%20aren't%20publicly%20available%20either%2C%20Wischer%20added%2C%20explaining%20that%20it's%20hard%20to%20ensure%20critical%20mineral%20stockpiling%20is%20happening%20correctly%20if%20people%20do%20not%20know%20exactly%20how%20many%20minerals%20are%20used%20in%20an%20average%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReleasing%20that%20kind%20of%20data%2C%20he%20said%2C%20would%20increase%20public%20reassurance%20concerning%20wartime%20preparation.%20%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20have%20ten-times%20that%20stockpile%20amount%20for%20a%20potential%20conflict%20because%20we%20would%20be%20going%20through%20munitions%20so%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22420ba193-0f4b-4168-98a5-dc7ae15ecbd0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20the%20stockpile%20matters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Defense%20released%20its%20first-ever%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defense.gov%2FNews%2FNews-Stories%2FArticle%2FArticle%2F3644527%2Fdod-releases-first-defense-industrial-strategy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Defense%20Industrial%20Strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%20to%20improve%20the%20resilience%20of%20the%20American%20military%20supply%20chain%2C%20in%20part%20by%20increasing%20stockpiles%20of%20critical%20minerals.%20Submarines%2C%20fighter%20aircraft%2C%20magnets%20used%20in%20missiles%2C%20radar%20systems%2C%20and%20drones%20all%20require%20critical%20earth%20minerals%20for%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20past%20report%20for%20Congress%20on%20rare%20earth%20minerals%20for%20national%20defense%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20noted%20that%20a%20single%20Virginia-class%20submarine%20requires%209%2C200%20pounds%20of%20rare%20earth%20minerals%2C%20while%20an%20Arleigh%20Burke-class%20destroyer%20requires%205%2C200%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Arleigh%20Burke%20class%20destroyer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5acbd276f41c7831008b4d99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22827%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EArleigh%20Burke-class%20destroyers%20USS%20Preble%20(DDG%2088)%2C%20USS%20Halsey%20(DDG%2097)%20and%20USS%20Sampson%20(DDG%20102)%20underway%20in%20the%20Arabian%20Gulf.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20partnerships%20with%20Pacific%20allies%20for%20mineral%20mining%20and%20processing%20are%20options%20for%20decreasing%20US%20reliance%20on%20China%20during%20peacetime%2C%20but%20Wischer%20argued%20that%20relying%20on%20safe%20ocean%20supply%20lines%20to%20move%20processed%20or%20raw%20minerals%20might%20not%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20sense%20when%20preparing%20for%20or%20waging%20a%20war%20in%20the%20Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20relying%20heavily%20on%20Japan%20and%20South%20Korea%20for%20these%20refined%20elements%2C%26quot%3B%20Wischer%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20we%20get%20into%20a%20potential%20conflict%20%5Bin%20the%20Pacific%5D%2C%20those%20supply%20chains%20are%20in%20no%20way%20guaranteed%20to%20have%20safe%20transport%20to%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%20That%20makes%20the%20stockpile%20even%20more%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20congressional%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcrsreports.congress.gov%2Fproduct%2Fpdf%2FR%2FR47833%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20late%20last%20year%20noted%20the%202023%20stockpile%20report%20to%20Congress%2C%20which%20is%20not%20public%2C%20%26quot%3Bdiscovered%20net%20shortfalls%20in%2088%20materials%2C%20valued%20at%20%2414.83%20billion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d7e1b0df-a8e5-4ecd-ac46-d6ebc9a1755f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENecessary%20for%20more%20than%20just%20defense%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20military%20has%20said%20that%20it%20aims%20to%20have%20%26quot%3Ba%20sustainable%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defense.gov%2FNews%2FNews-Stories%2FArticle%2FArticle%2F3700059%2Fdod-looks-to-establish-mine-to-magnet-supply-chain-for-rare-earth-materials%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emine-to-magnet%20supply%20chain%3C%2Fa%3E%20capable%20of%20supporting%20all%20US%20defense%20requirements%20by%202027.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bmine-to-magnet%26quot%3B%20effort%20%E2%80%94%20the%20naming%20for%20which%20is%20based%20on%20the%20military%20logistics%20phrase%20from%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dla.mil%2FAbout-DLA%2FNews%2FEnergy%2FArticle%2F823894%2Ffactory-to-foxhole%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efactory%20to%20foxhole%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20DoD%20awarded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defense.gov%2FNews%2FReleases%2FRelease%2FArticle%2F2941793%2Fdod-awards-35-million-to-mp-materials-to-build-us-heavy-rare-earth-separation-c%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2420%20million%20to%20a%20company%20called%20MP%20Materials%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20start%20processing%20and%20refining%20rare%20earth%20minerals%20at%20the%20company's%20mine%20in%20California%2C%20the%20largest%20rare%20earth%20minerals%20operation%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20the%20Australian-based%20mining%20company%20Lynas%20USA%20has%20been%20awarded%20nearly%20%24260%20million%20from%20the%20DoD%20to%20build%20a%20rare%20earth%20processing%20facility%20in%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unknown%20when%20US-based%20mining%20operations%20might%20be%20able%20to%20operate%20at%20a%20high%20enough%20capacity%20to%20offset%20Chinese%20imports.%20For%20now%2C%20US-based%20mining%20operations%20can't%20produce%20enough%20minerals%20to%20replace%20Chinese%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Virginia-class%20fast-attack%20submarine%20USS%20Vermont%20(SSN%20792)%20arrives%20at%20its%20new%20homeport%20of%20Joint%20Base%20Pearl%20Harbor-Hickam%2C%20July%2027%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fc945c4af076d3cf928cef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Virginia-class%20fast-attack%20submarine%20USS%20Vermont%20(SSN%20792)%20at%20its%20new%20homeport%20of%20Joint%20Base%20Pearl%20Harbor-Hickam.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%201st%20Class%20Chris%20Williamson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFabian%20Villalobos%2C%20an%20engineer%20and%20defense%20supply%20chain%20expert%20with%20the%20RAND%20Corporation%2C%20said%20that%20compared%20to%20some%20other%20industries%2C%20the%20US%20military%20is%20a%20relatively%20minor%20consumer%20of%20critical%20minerals.%20Industries%20such%20as%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.energy.gov%2Ffecm%2Frare-earth-elements%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMany%2520advanced%2520technologies%2520have%2520components%2Cpetroleum%2520refining%252C%2520and%2520consumer%2520electronics.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20healthcare%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20petroleum%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20consumer%20electronics%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wri.org%2Finsights%2Fcritical-minerals-us-climate-goals%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epush%20toward%20green%20energy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20all%20depend%20heavily%20on%20these%20minerals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20National%20Defense%20Stockpile%2C%20or%20the%20NDS%2C%20is%20the%20Nation's%20stockpile%20for%20strategic%20and%20critical%20materials%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20DoD's%20Deputy%20Assistant%20Secretary%20for%20Industrial%20Base%20Resilience%20Halimah%20Najieb-Locke%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2F118%2Fchrg%2FCHRG-118hhrg54313%2FCHRG-118hhrg54313.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econgressional%20hearing%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20stockpiles%20serve%20%26quot%3Bas%20an%20important%20buffer%20during%20emergencies.%20Stockpile%20reserves%20allow%20us%20to%20release%20materials%20to%20keep%20key%20production%20lines%20operating%20until%20long-term%20supply%20chains%20are%20restored.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20same%20testimony%2C%20Najieb-Lo