0EM%20with%20a%200.49%20rating.%20India%20ranks%2072%20in%20a%20total%20of%20174%20countries%2C%20with%20Bangladesh%20(0.38)%20on%20113%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20(0.43)%20on%2092%2C%20and%20China%20(0.63)%20on%2031.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fc4qmign8_ai-imf-index_625x300_27_June_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rating%20for%20each%20country%20is%20given%20based%20on%20the%20assessment%20of%20readiness%20in%20four%20key%20areas%20-%20digital%20infrastructure%2C%20human%20capital%20and%20labour%20market%20policies%2C%20innovation%20and%20economic%20integration%2C%20and%20regulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Foaha47g_ai-imf-index_625x300_27_June_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20IMF%20published%20a%20blog%20based%20on%20their%20research%20paper%20on%2014%20January%2C%20stating%20that%20AI%20could%20endanger%2033%20percent%20of%20jobs%20in%20AEs%2C%2024%20percent%20in%20EMs%2C%20and%2018%20percent%20in%20LICs.%20Overall%2C%2040%20percent%20of%20the%20jobs%20around%20the%20world%20will%20be%20affected%20by%20AI%2C%20replacing%20some%20and%20complimenting%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20brighter%20side%2C%20it%20also%20brings%20enormous%20potential%20to%20enhance%20the%20productivity%20of%20existing%20jobs%20for%20which%20AI%20can%20be%20a%20complementary%20tool%20and%20to%20create%20new%20jobs%20and%20even%20new%20industries%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Economist%20Giovanni%20Melina%2C%20in%20the%20IMF%20article%20from%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20most%20scenarios%2C%20AI%20will%20likely%20worsen%20overall%20inequality%2C%20a%20troubling%20trend%20that%20policymakers%20can%20work%20to%20prevent.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20the%20dashboard%20is%20a%20response%20to%20significant%20interest%20from%20our%20stakeholders%20in%20accessing%20the%20index.%20It%20is%20a%20resource%20for%20policymakers%2C%20researchers%2C%20and%20the%20public%20to%20better%20assess%20AI%20preparedness%20and%2C%20importantly%2C%20to%20identify%20the%20actions%20and%20design%20the%20policies%20needed%20to%20help%20ensure%20that%20the%20rapid%20gains%20of%20AI%20can%20benefit%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Melina.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719489540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fjg5gstu_imfeconomylogo_625x300_13_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Finternational-monetary-fund-maps-174-countries-artificial-intelligence-readiness-india-is-at-72-5980742%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20released%20an%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20Preparedness%20Index%20Dashboard%20on%20their%20website%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20tracking%20174%20economies%20globally%20for%20AI%20readiness.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Finternational-monetary-fund-maps-174-countries-artificial-intelligence-readiness-india-is-at-72-5980742%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Finternational-monetary-fund-maps-174-countries-artificial-intelligence-readiness-india-is-at-72-5980742%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Finternational-monetary-fund-maps-174-countries-artificial-intelligence-readiness-india-is-at-72-5980742%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cannes%20Critics%E2%80%99%20Week%20Title%20%E2%80%98Baby%E2%80%99%20Scoops%20Further%20Sale