icated%2C%20making%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20government%20versus%20Opposition%20acrimony%20is%20likely%20to%20escalate.%20An%20announcement%20is%20likely%20soon%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20government%20is%20likely%20to%20take%20a%20hard%20line%20after%20the%20%26quot%3Bbreakdown%20of%20trust%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20Opposition%20during%20the%20dialogue%20yesterday%20over%20the%20Speaker%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20also%20the%20question%20of%20keeping%20allies%20like%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20happy.%20Both%20had%20their%20eyes%20on%20the%20Speaker%20post%20as%20insurance%20for%20any%20split%20in%20their%20parties.%20But%20the%20BJP%20had%20refused%20to%20relent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20speculation%20that%20this%20time%2C%20the%20post%20might%20go%20to%20Me%20Naidu's%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party.%20TDP's%20GMC%20Balayogi%20was%20the%20Speaker%20when%20the%20NDA%20under%20Atal%20Bihar%20Vajpayee%20was%20in%20power%20and%20there%20is%20expectation%20that%20the%20post%20can%20now%20go%20to%20his%20son%20Harish%20Balayogi.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20peace%20offering%20to%20the%20TDP%20might%20keep%20NDA's%20internal%20harmony%20intact%2C%20it%20could%20bode%20trouble%20from%20another%20direction%2C%20by%20making%20the%20new%20muscular%2C%20combative%20Opposition%20extremely%20unhappy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%2C%20failing%20to%20get%20the%20spot%20of%20the%20Pro%20Tem%20Speaker%20had%20been%20angling%20for%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker%20post%2C%20which%20traditionally%20goes%20to%20it.%20But%20with%20the%20government%20brushing%20off%20its%20demands%20and%20its%20claim%2C%20they%20had%20forced%20a%20last-minute%20contest%20on%20the%20Speaker%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20loss%20was%20a%20given%2C%20in%20view%20of%20the%20government's%20numerical%20strength.%20But%20the%20Opposition%20insisted%20that%20it%20was%20out%20to%20send%20a%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20is%20the%20final%20arbiter%20of%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20people%2C%20the%20Congress%20asserted.%20Its%20new%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20pointedly%20said%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bconfident%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20Speaker%20would%20%26quot%3Ballow%20us%20to%20speak%2C%20to%20represent%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20that%20you%20can%20run%20the%20House%20efficiently%20by%20silencing%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20Opposition%20is%20a%20non-democratic%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThis%20election%20has%20shown%20that%20the%20people%20of%20India%20expect%20the%20Opposition%20to%20defend%20the%20constitution%E2%80%A6%20we%20are%20confident%20that%20by%20allowing%20Opposition%20to%20speak%2C%20you%20will%20do%20your%20duty%20of%20defending%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20government%2C%20while%20seeking%20consensus%20for%20their%20Speaker%20candidate%20Om%20Birla%2C%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20they%20were%20not%20considering%20a%20Deputy%20Speaker%20post%2C%20or%20the%20Opposition's%20claim%20to%20it%2C%20for%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20irked%20the%20Opposition%2C%20which%20fielded%20K%20Suresh%20%E2%80%93%20their%20seniormost%20parliamentarian%20and%20one%20hey%20thought%20would%20be%20the%20obvious%20choice%20for%20the%20Pro%20Tem%20Speaker%20--%20against%20Om%20Birla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20morning's%20events%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BRajnath%20Singh%20called%20(Congress%20chief)%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20extend%20support...%20entire%20Opposition%20said%20we%20will%20support%20but%20convention%20is%20Deputy%20Speaker%20should%20be%20from%20our%20side.%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20he%20would%20call%20back...%20but%20he%20has%20not%20yet...%20PM%20is%20asking%20for%20cooperation%20but%20our%20leader%20is%20getting%20insulted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20term%20of%20the%20NDA%20government%2C%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker%20was%20then%20ally%20AIADMK's%20M%20Thambidurai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Congress%20leader%20K%20Suresh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20(the%20BJP)%20denied%20(the%20post%20to)%20us%20in%20the%20last%20two%20terms%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20saying%20that%20you%20are%20not%20the%20recognised%20Opposition.%20Now%2C%20we%20are%20recognised%20as%20the%20Opposition.%20Deputy%20Speaker%20post%20is%20our%20right%2C%20but%20they%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20give%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719487860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F9mga7t98_lok-sabha-generic-ani-_625x300_26_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnda-likely-to-keep-lok-sabha-deputy-speakers-post-announcement-soon-sources-5981770%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20post%20of%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker%20post%2C%20vacant%20in%20the%20second%20term%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20will%20be%20filled%20again.%20But%20in%20another%20break%20from%20tradition%2C%20the%20incumbent%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20from%20the%20NDA%20and%20not%20the%20Opposition%2C%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnda-likely-to-keep-lok-sabha-deputy-speakers-post-announcement-soon-sources-5981770%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnda-likely-to-keep-lok-sabha-deputy-speakers-post-announcement-soon-sources-5981770%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnda-likely-to-keep-lok-sabha-deputy-speakers-post-announcement-soon-sources-5981770%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20watch%20India%20vs.%20England%3A%20Live%20stream%20T20%20World%20Cup%20semis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20yo