Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20Magistrate%20Tushar%20Singla%20said%20the%20bridge%20was%20built%20in%202011%20over%20Madiya%2C%20a%20small%20tributary%20that%20connects%20the%20Kankai%20river%20to%20the%20Mahananda.%20%26quot%3BHeavy%20rainfall%20in%20the%20catchment%20area%20in%20Nepal%20has%20led%20to%20a%20sudden%20rise%20in%20the%20water%20level.%20One%20of%20the%20pillars%20of%20the%20bridge%20could%20not%20withstand%20the%20strong%20current%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20incidents%20of%20bridge%20collapse%20were%20reported%20last%20week%20from%20Siwan%20and%20Araria%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2019%2C%20a%20portion%20of%20an%20under-construction%20bridge%20over%20the%20Bakra%20river%20in%20Bihar's%20Araria%20district%2C%20collapsed%20even%20before%20it%20was%20inaugurated.%20The%20bridge%2C%20built%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2012%20crore%2C%20came%20apart%20in%20seconds.%20Horrifying%20videos%20from%20the%20spot%20showed%20the%20huge%20chunks%20of%20concrete%20being%20washed%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Bihar%20%7C%20A%20portion%20of%20a%20bridge%20over%20the%20Bakra%20River%20has%20collapsed%20in%20Araria%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FstjDO2Xkq3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FstjDO2Xkq3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1803033213998391359%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2018%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20a%20number%20of%20similar%20incidents%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20state%2C%20leading%20to%20questions%2