rabhas-starrer%2Farticleshow%2F111313595.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBI%20Makes%20First%20Arrests%20In%20Bihar%20In%20NEET-UG%20Paper%20Leak%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20has%20made%20its%20first%20arrests%20in%20the%20NEET-UG%20paper%20leak%20case%20in%20Bihar%2C%20detaining%20two%20individuals%20from%20Patna%2C%20identified%20as%20Manish%20Kumar%20and%20Ashutosh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CBI%20sources%2C%20Manish%20Kumar%20facilitated%20the%20transportation%20of%20students%20in%20his%20car%20and%20is%20suspected%20of%20providing%20the%20use%20of%20an%20empty%20school%20where%20at%20least%20two%20dozen%20students%20were%20given%20the%20leaked%20paper%20and%20memorised%20it%2C%20while%20Ashutosh%20provided%20lodging%20for%20the%20students%20at%20his%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20men%20had%20been%20called%20by%20the%20agency%20for%20questioning%20on%20Thursday%20and%20they%20were%20arrested%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20has%20registered%20six%20First%20Information%20Reports%20(FIRs)%20in%20the%20NEET%20paper%20leak%20case%20with%20the%20first%20being%20on%20Sunday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20announced%20that%20the%20investigation%20would%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20central%20agency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20CBI%20arrests%2C%20the%20police%20had%20also%20taken%20some%20people%20into%20custody%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Delhi.%20These%20included%20an%20aspirant%20who%20said%20he%20and%20a%20few%20others%20had%20got%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20question%20paper%20a%20day%20before%20the%20exam.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%2024%20lakh%20students%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20NEET-UG%202024%20for%20undergraduate%20medical%20courses%2C%20which%20is%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%2C%20on%20May%205.%20The%20results%20were%20annou