he%20Chair%20is%20unprecedented%20in%20the%20annals%20of%20the%20history%20of%20Parliament.%20This%2C%20coming%20from%20the%20Chair%2C%20as%20one%20of%20the%20first%20duties%20of%20a%20newly%20elected%20Speaker%2C%20assumes%20even%20greater%20proportions%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20letter%20addressed%20to%20the%20Speake%2C%20signed%20by%20KC%20Venugopal%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20many%20things%20were%20discussed...%20about%20functioning%20of%20Parliament.%20Of%20course%20this%20issue%20also%20came%20up%20and%20Rahul%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20as%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20told%20the%20Speaker%20the%20reference%20could%20have%20been%20avoided.%20It%20was%20clearly%20a%20political%20reference...%20it%20could%20have%20been%20avoided%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Venugopal%20told%20press%20this%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Said%20On%20Emergency%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Birla's%20jabs%20Wednesday%20-%20he%20did%20not%20name%20the%20Congress%20but%20the%20reference%20was%20obvious%20-%20shattered%20what%20little%20goodwill%20crept%20into%20its%20relationship%20with%20the%20BJP%20following%20his%20re-election%20as%20the%20Speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20House%20after%20his%20election%2C%20Mr%20Birla%20called%20for%20two%20minutes'%20silence%20to%20remember%20%26quot%3Bthe%20determination%20of%20all%20those%20who%20opposed%20Emergency%26quot%3B%20and%20flayed%20the%20government%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndas-om-birla-wins-rare-contest-for-lok-sabha-speaker-5972066%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpeaker's%202-Minute%20Silence%20On%20Emergency%20Triggers%20Protests%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20this%20day%20then-Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20imposed%20an%20Emergency...%20and%20attacked%20the%20Constitution.%20Democratic%20values%20and%20debate%2