ember%20of%20the%20Vokkaliga%20community%2C%20is%20only%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20the%20Siddaramaiah-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20those%20speaking%20to%20papers%20(newspaper%20or%20media)%20go%20and%20speak%20to%20high%20command%2C%20get%20a%20solution%20and%20come.%20Let%20them%20go%20and%20get%20whatever%20solution%20they%20want.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20discuss%20before%20the%20media.%20I%20will%20also%20not%20discuss%20anything%20before%20the%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20said%2C%20making%20no%20secret%20of%20his%20displeasure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20anyone%20go%20and%20get%20whatever%20solution%20they%20want%2C%20who%20will%20say%20don't%3F%20Neither%20newspapers%20nor%20TV%20channels%20will%20give%20a%20solution%20for%20this%2C%20you%20(media)%20only%20give%20publicity%2C%20that's%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20regarding%20demand%20from%20some%20quarters%20in%20the%20party%20about%20the%20need%20to%20change%20the%20KPCC%20(state%20Congress)%20President%20--%20the%20post%20he%20currently%20holds%2C%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bvery%20happy%2C%20they%20should%20not%20waste%20time%2C%20they%20should%20go%20and%20find%20a%20solution%20for%20it....let%20them%20go%20and%20find%20solution%20from%20wherever%20they%20want%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20any%20objection.%26quot%3B%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20has%20apparently%20urged%20ministers%20not%20to%20issue%20statements%20seeking%20additional%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20posts%20in%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20is%20said%20to%20have%20spoken%20to%20Minister%20KN%20Rajanna%2C%20who%20is%20in%20the%20forefront%20with%20such%20a%20demand%2C%20over%20the%20phone%20and%20cautioned%20him%20against%20making%20any%20more%20public%20statements%20on%20the%20issue.%20He%20opined%20that%20public%20statements%20on%20this%20would%20negatively%20impact%20the%20government%20and%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20within%20the%20Congress%20is%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20the%20statement%20by%20the%20Ministers%20seeking%20three%20more%20Deputy%20CMs%2C%20was%20part%20of%20a%20plan%20by%20Siddaramaiah's%20camp%20to%20keep%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20in%20check%2C%20amid%20talks%20he%20might%20seek%20the%20CM%20post%20after%20two-and-half%20years%20of%20this%20government's%20tenure%2C%20and%20to%20counter%20his%20influence%20both%20in%20the%20government%20and%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECo-operation%20Minister%20Rajanna%2C%20Housing%20Minister%20B%20Z%20Zameer%20Ahmed%20Khan%2C%20Public%20Works%20Minister%20Satish%20Jarkiholi%20and%20a%20couple%20of%20others%20--%20all%20considered%20to%20be%20close%20to%20Siddaramaiah%20--%20earlier%20this%20week%20once%20again%20raised%20the%20pitch%20for%20three%20more%20Deputy%20CMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20decided%20that%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bthe%20only%26quot%3B%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20amid%20stiff%20competition%20between%20him%20and%20Siddaramaiah%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20post%20after%20the%20Assembly%20election%20results%20in%20May%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20party%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20said%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bcommitment%26quot%3B%20made%20by%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20to%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20while%20convincing%20him%20to%20give%20up%20his%20claim%20for%20the%20CM%20post%20and%20to%20take%20up%20the%20role%20of%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20leaders%20in%20Mr%20Shivakumar's%20camp%20too%20seem%20to%20have%20started%20coming%20out%20openly%20in%20support%20of%20their%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChannagiri%20Congress%20MLA%20Basavaraju%20V%20Shivaganga%20on%20Wednesday%20urged%20the%20party%20to%20make%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajanna%2C%20also%20hinting%20about%20t