9s%20what%20a%20good%20parent%20is%20required%20to%20do.%20If%20you%20are%20soft%2C%20your%20children%20are%20going%20to%20%E2%80%9Csit%20on%20your%20head%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EParents%20feel%20liberated%20when%20they%20discover%20that%20there%20are%20positive%20ways%20to%20discipline%20their%20children%20as%20well.%20Changing%20and%20breaking%20established%20patterns%20is%20not%20easy.%20It%20takes%20hard%20work%20but%20once%20they%20make%20the%20change%2C%20they%20share%20with%20delight%20how%20connection%20and%20collaboration%20with%20the%20child%20works%20much%20better%20than%20force.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%224%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmpathy%20is%20key%20to%20building%20trust%20and%20connection%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20does%20my%20child%20lie%20to%20me%20and%20hide%20things%20from%20me%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20a%20question%20most%20parents%20ask.%20They%20long%20for%20an%20open%20and%20honest%20relationship%20with%20their%20child.%20Children%20lie%20or%20hide%20things%20to%20avoid%20the%20consequences%20of%20authority%20or%20punishment%20(simply%20to%20protect%20themselves).%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThey%20also%20learn%20early%20in%20life%20that%20parents%20rarely%20understand%20their%20point%20of%20view.%20Parents%20who%20have%20learned%20to%20listen%20and%20empathise%20with%20their%20children%20have%20found%20this%20to%20be%20a%20game%20changer.%20Typically%2C%20when%20their%20kids%20were%20upset%20they%20would%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20cry%20or%20don%E2%80%99t%20make%20a%20fuss.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBut%20now%20they%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20know%20this%20is%20hard%20for%20you.%20I%20can%20see%20how%20disappointed%2Fsad%20you%20are.%E2%80%9D%20This%20instantly%20makes%20the%20child%20feel%20understood%20and%20they%20are%20more%20open%20and%20trusting%20with%20their%20parents.%20This%20also%20builds%20their%20emotional%20intelligence%20where%20they%20learn%20how%20to%20handle%20feelings%20in%20a%20healthy%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeeting%20needs%20changes%20kids%E2%80%99%20behaviour%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%93%20What%20every%20parent%20wishes%20for%20is%20a%20magic%20wand%20to%20make%20their%20child%20%E2%80%9Cbehave%E2%80%9D.%20They%20actually%20have%20one%3A%20understanding%20the%20reason%20behind%20behaviours.%20When%20we%20meet%20our%20children%E2%80%99s%20needs%2C%20their%20behaviour%20changes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EParents%20find%20it%20valuable%20to%20make%20the%20shift%20from%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20behave%20like%20this%E2%80%9D%20to%20playing%C2%A0%20detective%20and%20asking%20themselves%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20my%20child%20doing%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20This%20has%20helped%20a%20great%20number%20of%20parents%20defuse%20situations%20that%20could%20have%20turned%20explosive!%20They%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CKnowing%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334684%2Fmumbai-ca-dad-starts-a-toy-rental-business-rents-affordable-toys-for-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echild%E2%80%99s%20developmental%20needs%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20must%20for%20every%20parent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2F1_11zon-1-1719403506.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lessons%20from%20parenting%20workshops%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2F1_11zon-1-1719403506.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2F1_11zon-1-1719403506-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterind