%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Assam%2C%20there%20are%202%2C500%20islands%20and%20most%20of%20them%20are%20inhabited.%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20on%20an%20idea%20that%20involved%20the%20support%20of%20local%20people%20and%20the%20state%20government%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20these%20people%20and%20improve%20the%20health%20conditions%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20vulnerable%20communities%2C%20especially%20the%20women%20and%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%E2%80%99t%20build%20roads%20everywhere%20and%20certainly%20can%E2%80%99t%20have%20helicopters%20give%20services%20throughout%20the%20year.%20So%2C%20we%20shifted%20to%20the%20traditional%20system%20of%20using%20boats%20and%20to%20look%20upon%20the%20river%20as%20an%20ally%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sanjoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20collaboration%20with%20the%20National%20Rural%20Health%20Mission%2C%20the%20non-profit%20launched%20the%20boat%20clinics%20in%202005%20to%20bridge%20the%20healthcare%20divide.%20Since%20then%2C%20monthly%20health%20camps%20have%20been%20organised%20across%2014%20districts%20including%20Dibrugarh%2C%20Tinsukia%2C%20Jorhat%2FMajuli%2C%20Sonitpur%2C%20and%20Nalbari.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20purpose%2C%2015%20such%20floating%20health%20clinics%20are%20operating%20along%20the%20river%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20isolated%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20month%2C%20a%20team%20comprising%20two%20medical%20officers%2C%20laboratory%20technician%2C%20pharmacist%2C%20and%20three%20nurses%20reach%20out%20to%20offer%20primary%20healthcare%20at%20the%20island%20itself.%20These%20boat%20clinics%20are%20equipped%20with%20vaccines%20for%20newborn%20babies%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20measles%2C%20Japanese%20encephalitis%2C%20polio%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20conducts%20routine%20immunisations%20for%20pregnant%20women%20and%20also%20has%20a%20provision%20to%20test%20haemoglobin%2C%20blood%20glucose%20levels%2C%