0from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fshingles%2Fvaccination.html%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fshingles%2Fvaccination.html%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Accessed%202nd%20May%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ECDC%20Understanding%20How%20Vaccines%20Work.%20Available%20from%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fvaccines%2Fhcp%2Fconversations%2Funderstanding-vacc-work.html%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fvaccines%2Fhcp%2Fconversations%2Funderstanding-vacc-work.html%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Photo%20credit%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.myvaccinationhub.in%5C%22%3Ehttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.myvaccinationhub.in%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719311809000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIn-betweeen-article-image_GSK-1-1719303286.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D354182%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you%E2%80%99re%20above%2050%20and%20have%20had%20chickenpox%20before%2C%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20of%20developing%20shingles%20%E2%80%94%20a%20viral%20infection%20caused%20by%20the%20varicella-zoster%20virus%20(VZV).%20The%20best%20way%20to%20prevent%20it%20is%20with%20the%20vaccination.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20all%20about%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TBI%20Team%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354182%2Fshingles-symptoms-treatment-vaccination-chickenpox-virus-glaxosmithkline-pharmaceutical-vaccine%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Feel%20Like%20a%20King%E2%80%99%3A%20Farmer%20Earns%20Rs%2015%20Lakh%2FAcre%20by%20Making%20a%20Switch%20From%20Rubber%20Cultivation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKerala%20is%20the%20largest%20rubber%20producer%20in%20the%20country.%20More%20than%20a%20decade%20back%2C%20its%20rubber%20production%20started%20falling%20as%20growers%20found%20it%20unprofitable%20owing%20to%20rising%20production%20costs%20and%20falling%20prices%20amid%20cheap%20imports%20from%20Vietnam%20and%20Indonesia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBordering%20Karnataka%2C%20Ulikkal%20village%20in%20the%20Kannur%20district%20was%20a%20lush%20landscape%20that%20was%20once%20predominantly%20a%20rubber-growing%20area.%20Among%20millions%20of%20rubber%20farmers%2C%20Biju%20Narayanan%E2%80%99s%20family%20who%20cultivated%20rubber%20on%20one-third%20of%20the%20farmland%2C%20also%20lost%20their%20major%20income%20source%20with%20plummeting%20profitability.%20It%20became%20costlier%20to%20produce%20rubber%20than%20to%20sell%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20cost%20of%20production%20was%20around%20Rs%20160%20per%20kg%20and%20the%20selling%20price%20was%20Rs%20110%20per%20kg.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20rates%20in%20rubber%20were%20dwindling%20as%20farmers%20could%20fetch%20only%20Rs%20100%20per%20kg%20from%20rubber.%20A%20labourer%20could%20earn%20more%20wages%20daily.%20It%20was%20not%20sufficient%20for%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiju%20reconsidered%20the%20agricultural%20practices%20and%20made%20the%20bold%20decision%20to%20replace%20seven%20acres%20of%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20rubber%20trees%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295835%2Fcoconut-farmer-senior-citizen-grows-mangosteen-from-malaysia-exports-to-gulf-countries%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexotic%20fruits%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20rambutan%2C%20mangosteen%2C%20pepper%2C%20areca%20nut%2C%20coconut%2C%20cashew%2C%20and%20other%20crops.%20%E2%80%9CI%20axed%20most%20of%20the%20rubber%20trees%20to%20try%20new%20plantations.%20People%20called%20me%20a%20madman%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20the%20progressive%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3