e%20our%20daughter%20with%20a%20better%20life.%20Every%20day%2C%20we%20would%20hear%20news%20about%20food%20adulteration%20which%20deeply%20concerned%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aseem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAseem%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20general%20manager%20at%20ITC%2C%20and%20Neetu%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20MakeMyTrip%2C%20were%20already%20familiar%20with%20the%20hotel%20industry.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20community%20and%20a%20home%20where%20people%20could%20come%20to%20take%20a%20break%20from%20city%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20was%20already%20in%20love%20with%20the%20mountains%20and%20which%20place%20was%20better%20than%20%E2%80%98The%20Queen%20Of%20Hills%E2%80%99%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20to%20look%20for%20places%20before%20deciding%20to%20move.%20One%20thing%20that%20we%20noticed%20was%20that%20the%20hill%20station%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20big%20buildings%20but%20we%20did%20not%20want%20that.%20We%20wanted%20to%20give%20a%20break%20to%20people%20from%20the%20hustle%20and%20bustle%20of%20cities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-2-1718977526.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aseem%20and%20Neetu%20Varma%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-2-1718977526.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-2-1718977526-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-2-1718977526-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-2-1718977526-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebe