%3Cp%3EWhat%20lay%20at%20the%20core%20of%20the%20Brigadiar%E2%80%99s%20Cottage%20was%20sustainability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEverything%20%E2%80%94%20from%20what%20we%20use%20to%20make%20our%20home%20and%20what%20we%20serve%20to%20the%20guests%20%E2%80%94%20we%20wanted%20it%20all%20to%20be%20as%20eco-friendly%20as%20we%20could.%20We%20did%20not%20use%20any%20cement%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20house.%20We%20used%20only%20locally-sourced%20materials%20and%20hired%20local%20artists%20to%20do%20the%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAseem%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20not%20only%20provided%20jobs%20for%20the%20locals%20but%20also%20reduced%20the%20carbon%20footprint%20we%20would%20have%20created.%20Although%20we%20cannot%20use%20it%20in%20the%20winters%2C%20we%20also%20have%20solar%20power%20in%20the%20homestay%2C%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20has%20also%20planted%20300%20trees%20ever%20since%20they%20purchased%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Neetu%20and%20Aseem%20have%20a%20poultry%20farm%2C%20a%20dairy%20farm%2C%20an%20apiary%2C%20and%20an%20organic%20food%20forest.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353896%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENeetu%20and%20Aseem%20have%20a%20poultry%20farm%2C%20a%20dairy%20farm%2C%20an%20apiary%2C%20and%20an%20organic%20food%20forest.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20it%2C%20Neetu%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20was%20not%20just%20to%20create%20an%20escape%20for%20adults%20but%20also%20a%20space%20for%20the%20kids%20to%20explore%20nature.%20Today%E2%80%99s%20kids%20are%20drinking%20milk%20out%20of%20cartons%20and%20eating%20chicken%20from%20KFC.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20create%20an%20organic%20space%2C%20an%20organic%20lifestyle%20for%20not%20only%20our%20daughter%20but%20for%20all%20the%20kids%20we%20could%20offer%20it%20to.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEverything%20that%20we%20serve%20to%20the%20guests%20comes%20from%20our%20farms.%20We%20even%20make%20our%20own%20oil%20from%20walnuts%2C%20groundnuts%20and%20mustard%20seeds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeetu%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20produce%20our%20own%20honey%20with%2023%20bee%20boxes.%20We%20grow%20turmeric%20and%20chia%20seeds%20and%20have%20our%20own%20dairy%20for%20milk.%20Additionally%2C%20we%20maintain%20a%20small%20poultry%20farm%20with%20around%2030%20chickens%20for%20eggs.%20Vegetables%20are%20sourced%20from%20local%20farms%20as%20well.%20Essentially%2C%20everything%20we%20consume%20here%20is%20either%20grown%20or%20raised%20by%20us%20or%20sourced%20from%20the%20organic%20farms%20nearby.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F302308%2Fbengaluru-couple-grows-organic-food-forest-using-permaculture-build-sustainable-mud-house%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20homestay%20%3C%2Fa%3Ealso%20follows%20a%20no-waste%20policy.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20try%20to%20use%20everything%20that%20we%20procure.%20All%20the%20food%20waste%20becomes%20fodder%20for%20our%20livestock.%20All%20the%20cow%20dung%20is%20converted%20and%20made%20into%20organic%20incense%20sticks%20to%20be%20used%20in%20the%20homestay%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aseem%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC54wullSoM3%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC54wullSoM3%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC54wullSoM3%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Brigadiers%20Cottage%2C%20Mussoorie.%20(%40brigadierscottagemussoorie)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20spend%20time%20at%20the%20homestay%3F%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20guests%20come%20to%20stay%20with%20us%2C%20they%20usually%20book%20a%20three-night%20stay.%20On%20the%20first%20day%2C%20they%20arrive%20at%20the%20cottage%20by%20the%20afternoon%2C%20usually%20post-lunch%2C%20after%20a%20long%20drive%20from%20places%20like%20Delhi%20or%20Mumbai.%20We%20encourage%20them%20to%20settle%20down%20and%20relax%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aseem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20common%20dining%20area%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20the%20dining%20room%20or%20the%20terrace%2C%20then%20becomes%20a%20gathering%20spot%20in%20the%20evening.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20winter%2C%20we%20have%20bonfires%20to%20enhance%20the%20cosy%20atmosphere.%20On%20the%20second%20day%2C%20we%20recommend%20exploring%20the%20local%20sights%20like%20Landour%20and%20the%20Mall%20Road.%20Guests%20often%20spend%20the%20day%20sightseeing%20and%20enjoying%20the%20local%20attractions.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20third%20day%2C%20we%20ask%20the%20guests%20to%20visit%20the%20Benog%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary.%20We%20have%20a%20local%20guide%20who%20is%20very%20knowledgeable%20about%20herbs%20and%20the%20area.%20He%20takes%20the%20guests%20on%20a%20trail%20through%20the%20jungle%20to%20the%20waterfalls.%20Depending%20on%20their%20preference%2C%20the%20trail%20can%20be%20a%20short%20one-hour%20walk%20or%20a%20longer%20four-hour%20hike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20area%20is%20also%20a%20bird%20sanctuary%2C%20making%20it%20a%20paradise%20for%20bird%20watchers.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20guests%20have%20spotted%20rare%20birds%20such%20as%20the%20blue-throated%20barbet%2C%20plum-headed%20parakeet%2C%20and%20Himalayan%20bulbul%20from%20our%20cottage%2C%20and%20even%20more%20when%20they%20go%20on%20the%20trails.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20morning%20hike%20and%20bird%20watching%2C%20guests%20come%20back%20for%20breakfast%20and%20then%20head%20down%20to%20the%20Yamuna%20River.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadier