5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221519%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAkash%20learnt%20cooking%20from%20his%20mother%20and%20grandmother.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%2029-year-old%20Chennai%20resident%20only%20began%20cooking%20regularly%20after%20he%20left%20home%20for%20an%20internship%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20following%20his%20degree%20in%20architecture.%20It%20was%20there%20that%20he%20started%20to%20enjoy%20the%20process%20of%20cooking%20and%20appreciate%20its%20finer%20nuances.%20He%20found%20that%20cooking%20was%20a%20great%20way%20to%20unwind%20and%20destress%20after%20a%20long%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20it%20took%20him%20a%20few%20more%20years%20to%20realise%20that%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334496%2Fkashmir-rukhsaar-sayeed-masterchef-india-chef-khalis-frozen-foods%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrue%20passion%20lay%20in%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20he%20continued%20to%20experiment%20in%20different%20avenues.%20%E2%80%9CI%20worked%20as%20a%20teaching%20assistant%20at%20an%20architecture%20firm.%20I%20even%20did%20a%20diploma%20in%20animation%20to%20see%20if%20that%20excited%20me.%20After%20trying%20out%20different%20things%2C%20I%20came%20across%20a%20course%20%E2%80%94%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20food%20design%20in%20Milan%2C%20which%20interested%20me%20deeply%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20doing%20something%20in%20the%20food%20domain%20where%20he%20could%20use%20his%20creativity%20and%20artistry%20motivated%20Akash.%20After%20completing%20his%20degree%2C%20he%20spent%20a%20year%20travelling%20across%20Europe%2C%20engaging%20in%20various%20internships%20that%20helped%20him%20uncover%20his%20future%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20about%20how%20food%20is%20viewed%20outside%20India.%20I%20worked%20with%20a%20food%20designer%20in%20the%20Netherlands%